<HEAD>5-Year-Old Shot By Playmate While Playing `Robocop'</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LAKE WORTH, Fla. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A 7-year-old boy shot and wounded his
5-year-old playmate as they imitated characters in the movie
``Robocop,'' police said.
   Ronelis Frendeles was in guarded condition late Monday after
being wounded in both legs by a single gunshot, said police
spokeswoman Lori Nedzweckas.
