<HEAD>Father Pleads Innocent by Reason of Insanity in Daughter's Burning</HEAD>
<DATELINE>AKRON, Ohio (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A man pleaded innocent by reason of insanity
Tuesday to charges that he set his pregnant daughter on fire during
