<HEAD>For Release Weekend Editions Aug 19-20 and thereafter</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are Broadway's new and current shows. Ticket
supply as of Aug. 11 is indicated as Difficult or Available. Credit
card holders can order tickets by phone or by calling Telecharge or
Ticketron.
